[Exercise and cancer: Evidence of efficacy during and after treatments].

[Article in French]

Ninot G(1), Flori N(2), Huteau ME(2), Stoebner-Delbarre A(2), Senesse P(3).

Author information:
(1)Université de Montpellier, plateforme CEPS, équipe EA4556 Epsylon, 
