Symptom perception in heart failure - Interventions and outcomes: A scoping 
review.

Santos GC(1), Liljeroos M(2), Dwyer AA(3), Jaques C(4), Girard J(5), Strömberg 
A(6), Hullin R(7), Schäfer-Keller P(8).

